ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 230, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 230 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to SASKATCHEWAN with respect to the rainstorms that occurred from July 27 to 30, 2019.
